Package com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc

webMethods Adapter for SAP IDoc Java API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDocConstants
    This interface contains IDoc specific constants for the Adapter for SAP IDoc Java API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IDataDocument
    Class that represents an IDoc using IData to implement the IDocDocument interface.
    IDataDocumentList
    Class that holds and manages a list of IDoc documents using IData to implement the IDocDocumentList interface.
    IDataRecord
    Class that serves as a basic instance for accessing structured IDoc data elements using IData to implement the IDocRecord interface.
    IDataSegment
    Class that represents a single IDoc segment using IData to implement the IDocSegment interface.
    IDocDocumentList
    Class that holds and manages a list of IDoc documents to implement the IDocDocumentList interface.

Package com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc Description

webMethods Adapter for SAP IDoc Java API.

Provides the classes necessary to create an IDoc list with the Adapter for SAP and the classes needed to handle an IDoc list received from a SAP system that might get transfered to another Adapter for SAP.

This package basically provides an Adapter for SAP specific implementation of the SAP IDoc Class Library interfaces plus a wrapper of the JCoIDoc implementation that comes with the SAP IDoc Class library.

Since:
7.1
